To publish DocBook 5 documents to WebHelp with Feedback, use the DocBook WebHelp
        with Feedback transformation scenario. You can customize the out-of-the-box
      transformation by editing some of its parameters:

;

;

;



;

webhelp.product.version - this parameter specifies the documentation
          version. New comments are bound to this version. Multiple documentation versions can be
          deployed on the same server;

.
